title: Lady Indians win fifth consecutive region title; Newnan 3rd
text:
Champs – Again, again, again and again Lady Indians win fifth consecutive region title; Newnan 3rd by Comments 
East Coweta freshman Kelley Lynch (center) is all smiles after touching home plate on her third and final home run of this year’s Region 3- tournament. At left, senior Mekhia Freeman legs out a bunt single for one of her three hits in a 10-2 win over South Cobb. More
